WEBVTT

00:02:55.167 --> 00:03:00.268
because his boyfriend had outed him as gay

00:03:00.292 --> 00:03:03.518
to his extremely
conservative Korean family.

00:03:03.542 --> 00:03:08.667
So this is not just
men-spying-on-women issue.

00:03:10.292 --> 00:03:13.434
And I'm here to share

00:03:13.458 --> 00:03:15.875
what I learned from this experience.

00:03:16.833 --> 00:03:20.184
What I learned is that data leaks.

00:03:20.208 --> 00:03:22.143
It's like water.

00:03:22.167 --> 00:03:23.893
It gets in places you don't want it.

00:03:23.917 --> 00:03:25.184
Human leaks.

00:03:25.208 --> 00:03:27.351
Your friends give away
information about you.

00:03:27.375 --> 00:03:30.268
Your family gives away
information about you.